Interface OobErrorMessage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OobMessage, OobMessageMeta, OobOutgoingMessage

    public interface OobErrorMessage
extends OobOutgoingMessage, OobMessageMeta
    This object allow the client to send some error information to the server.

      • ERROR_CODE_CUSTOM_BASE

        static final int ERROR_CODE_CUSTOM_BASE
        Baseline for the application specific error codes. It is recommended to use this constant for definition of specific error codes.

        For example the custom error codes could be:
        - ERROR_CODE_CUSTOM_BASE + 0
        - ERROR_CODE_CUSTOM_BASE + 1
        - ERROR_CODE_CUSTOM_BASE + 2
        ...

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
